# Forecast engine

Located under app/server/services/forecast/* with extensive tests in __tests__.

## Modules (selected)

- ForecastEngine.ts — orchestrator
- DataLoaderService.ts — loads DB → in-memory cache
- ModernCacheService.ts — performance-optimized cache
- AccountRegisterService.ts — register-level operations
- ReoccurrenceService.ts — recurring schedule expansion and adjustments
- RegisterEntryService.ts — entry-level operations
- TransferService.ts — inter-register transfers and validations
- LoanCalculatorService.ts — interest and amortization calculations
- DateTimeService.ts, DateTime.ts — calendar and edge-case handling (weekends, DST, anchors)
- DataPersisterService.ts — writes cache back to DB
- reoccurrenceIntervals.ts — interval definitions
- lib/rateLimiter.ts — forecast loop rate limiting
- types.ts — shared types

## Testing

- Integration and regression suites under app/server/services/forecast/__tests__
- Run scripts:
  - pnpm test:forecast (custom runner)
  - pnpm test:forecast:unit and :integration

## Extending safely

- Keep modules single-responsibility and pure when possible; pass dependencies explicitly rather than importing global state
- Update types.ts for new concepts; add fixtures/tests first
- Ensure DataLoaderService and DataPersisterService are updated to include any new computed fields persisted
